OL,5, The city of Grenoble has gone to       
OL,6, France's highest administrative court  
OL,7, to challenge a ban imposed on a new    
OL,8, city rule allowing full-body "burkini" 
OL,9, swimsuits in public pools.             
OL,11,FGrenoble's decision to authorise all   
OL,12,Fswimwear, including burkinis, sparked a
OL,13,Flegal battle with the government.      
OL,15,FBurkinis are worn largely by Muslim    
OL,16,Fwomen, as a way of preserving modesty  
OL,17,Fand upholding their faith.             
OL,19,FBut religious expression in public life
OL,20,Fin France can be divisive.             
